Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! That's a whalesquid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't attack it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Interference from the seawater\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}is disrupting accurate targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hit it next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it be, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll just get more violent if you provoke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
