Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.89,0:02:49.77,epTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\pos(640,440)}A Soldier's Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now. I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The space guy came flying back earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he killed a whalesquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whalesquids have been considered\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}sacred creatures since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And he killed it for no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world were \Nyou thinking, Ledo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Folk are already starting to feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors are going around that this'll bring about a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering who did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,people will obviously be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{oi maji ka yo}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{dou nattenda}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all just superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For sailors, however, he just\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}committed the greatest taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only hope nothing bad will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Analyze this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Amplification and analysis of the DNA is estimated to take four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the probability of a result contradicting the unique wave signature is minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out if the Hideauze\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}on Earth have any unique traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the Hideauze have reached even Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could I have brought it here\N with me from space?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,While I can complete a biological analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot retrieve any information\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}regarding their invasion strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gather intel from the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to know their numbers and territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty well these days, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to take it easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and take a few days off every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to move to the main ship\N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}where it's a little more pastoral and—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I may not be\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}able to walk anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,my legs still remember\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}just how great this fleet is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes and ears still remember\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the people sailing along with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to continue to protect the smiles\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}and laughter of those who live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the proof that I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when you need to stay in bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems the fleet got\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}involved with a whalesquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For heaven's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how old you get,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,life will always be full of new experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you say you're not afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever reality gives us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it is our privilege to accept it while we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Privilege, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, should I become unable to lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I must pass the torch to my successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you guys heard about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The whalesquids' territory is full of treasures no one's ever seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,90,,And {\i1}we'll{\i0} be the ones taking 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.68,Default,,0,0,90,,Riches as far as the eye can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:02.90,Default,,0,0,90,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,90,,No one's ever dared brave a whalesquid nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,90,,Well, that's the thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,90,,How can you say there's a load of treasure if no one's been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.97,Default,,0,0,90,,But someone {\i1}did{\i0} go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,90,,He told me about it before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We're mechanics, not salvagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me someone fool enough to take on a whalesquid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.77,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here! That metalhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those monsters stand no chance against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You already have him on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have the basics covered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back once you got the space boy and his metalhead convinced!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you let this\N happen under your watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You let him attack a whalesquid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the ships' captains are feeling uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a whole list of people waiting for action to be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to make excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault for not telling him beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That means there are lots more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will do the same in\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}the future and do my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even understand\N what you're saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hideauze are a\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}threat to all of Mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Annihilating them is the\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}only possible option.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is nothing but your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no reason whatsoever to kill whalesquids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Real peace and prosperity cannot be achieved without eliminating every threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Gargantia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Commodore wants to hear the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. They're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to continue arguing in front of the Commodore?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll report to him, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You two may leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Flange!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me more about the Hideauze... The whalesquids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How many are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are their strengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are their weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a second, Ledo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still planning on doing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The whalesquids get really scary if you're aggressive towards them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but they won't attack unless provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel sorry for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They are enemies.\N They must be annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you not understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to keep up \Nyour stupid war here on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fight's got nothing to do with us! Don't drag us into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your civilization is very—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\p1\an7\fscx33\fscy23\pos(640,660)}m 276 20 l 264 20 l 264 -120 l 288 -120 l 288 20 l 276 20 m 288 20 l 312 20 l 312 -120 l 288 -120 l 288 -180 l 264 -180 l 264 -60 l 240 -60 l 240 20 l 264 20 l 264 80 l 288 80 l 288 20 m 368 20 l 356 20 l 356 -120 l 380 -120 l 380 20 l 368 20 m 380 20 l 404 20 l 404 -120 l 380 -120 l 380 -180 l 356 -180 l 356 -120 l 332 -120 l 332 -60 l 356 -60 l 356 80 l 380 80 l 380 20 m -92 20 l -104 20 l -104 -120 l -80 -120 l -80 20 l -92 20 m -80 20 l -56 20 l -56 -120 l -80 -120 l -80 -180 l -104 -180 l -104 -76 l -128 -76 l -128 20 l -104 20 l -104 80 l -80 80 l -80 20 m -12 80 l -12 80 l -12 -120 l 12 -120 l 12 20 l 12 20 m 12 20 l 36 20 l 36 -120 l 12 -120 l 12 -180 l -12 -180 l -12 -120 l -36 -120 l -36 80 l -12 80 l -12 80 l -12 80 l 12 20 m -184 20 l -196 20 l -196 -120 l -172 -120 l -172 20 l -184 20 m -172 20 l -148 20 l -149 -8 l -172 -8 l -172 -180 l -196 -180 l -196 -120 l -220 -120 l -220 20 l -196 20 l -196 80 l -172 80 l -172 20 m -368 20 l -380 20 l -380 -120 l -356 -120 l -356 20 l -368 20 m -356 20 l -332 20 l -332 -92 l -356 -92 l -356 -180 l -380 -180 l -380 -120 l -404 -120 l -404 20 l -380 20 l -380 80 l -356 80 l -356 20 m -276 20 l -288 20 l -288 -120 l -264 -120 l -264 20 l -276 20 m -264 -50 l -240 -50 l -240 -120 l -264 -120 l -264 -180 l -288 -180 l -288 -120 l -312 -120 l -312 20 l -288 20 l -288 80 l -264 80 l -264 20 m 92 20 l 80 20 l 80 -120 l 104 -120 l 104 20 l 92 20 m 104 20 l 128 20 l 128 -120 l 104 -120 l 104 -180 l 80 -180 l 80 -120 l 56 -120 l 56 -90 l 80 -90 l 80 80 l 104 80 l 104 20 m 184 20 l 172 20 l 172 -120 l 196 -120 l 196 20 l 184 20 m 196 -36 l 220 -36 l 220 -120 l 196 -120 l 196 -180 l 172 -180 l 172 -120 l 148 -120 l 148 20 l 172 20 l 172 80 l 196 80 l 196 20
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your civilization is so primitive that the Hideauze simply ignore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Confrontation is but a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, how do you intend to stand against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You neither have a specific plan of action,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,nor do you even think about the betterment of your civilization as a whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, you fight amongst yourselves despite being fellow humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When they attack,\N it will be too late to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill them before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I live to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do that to be yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion, if you're planning anything stupid, give up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna use Ledo and Chamber, and loot the whalesquids' territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to fight the whalesquids anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.84,0:11:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just be there to grab the treasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that means putting the fleet at risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you find might as well be trash if it doesn't help Gargantia in some way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's even explored the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all uncharted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Prizes beyond your wildest dreams are waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you feel your salvager blood boiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not interested\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}in your childish expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All you want to do is\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}inflate that ego of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even do it yourself,\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}so you get someone else to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're content with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you, Bellows!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I said I wanted\N to avenge my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That, too, is nothing but a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Any word from the Alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No response so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you determine our coordinates?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Further parallax measurements\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}of the planet's orbit are required.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The analysis of the biological\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}sample is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the result?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The exoskeleton has adapted\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}to the different environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but the genetic data is indistinguishable from the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the same species.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm correct to try and annihilate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I must do this for the people of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't they understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on linguistic analysis,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hypothesize that the\N Earthian survival strategy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is fundamentally different\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}from that of the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer for that question is not included in the standard dictionary of the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it exists in the Earthian language.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Coexistence and mutual prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The galaxy current's shining like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that the whalesquids?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Multiple underwater objects approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from their noise signature, they are likely to be Hideauze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sonar ping at 10 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a ton of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Depth at about thirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Double the patrols!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the defense vessels on standby beside the main fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To have so many come in such\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}shallow waters is unheard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Their trajectory will intersect with ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The whalesquids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole shoal's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,90,,Get it up! Get it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,90,,This is all because we let that alien stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,90,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:10.83,Default,,0,0,90,,Forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.36,Default,,0,0,90,,Calm your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the siren.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take command. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Commodore Fairlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A group of whalesquids is approaching the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they may be numerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,no harm will come to us\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}if we prepare accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to minimize provocation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we will now stop all of Gargantia's engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget, relay that to all the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any light or sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we halt the engines, citizens\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}are to remain wherever they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep noise to a minimum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the main power supply!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Move out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My fight has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean with the fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will not cause you any more trouble. I will leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want you doing something that dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you before.\N You must follow our directives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If the whalesquids attack the fleet, you are free to do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But until that time, you'll do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They are right under the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot do my duty as long as I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking Ledo and Chamber with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head out to the whalesquids' territory and do some salvaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd joke about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a list of people who've\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}signed up to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving Gargantia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Just approve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore, I'd also like to ask for\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}permission to leave with my ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Flange?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You too? But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You own so many ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you left, Gargantia's defenses\N would be left bare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The seabed holds the glorious\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}heritage of a bygone era.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I can retrieve even a bit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't hold it against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I will never agree to put all of Gargantia in danger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,for the personal gain\N{\alpha&HFF&}..{\r}of a few narrow-minded—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Call Dr. Ordum!
